s\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1070}, {\"ngram\": \"about 500,000 pounds\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The company also provided wool for the 2022 Winter Olympics in Beijing, and Carver's family property, Imperial Stock Ranch, supplied wool for the 2014 Winter Olympics in Sochi, Russia, and 2018 Winter Olympics in Pyeongchang, South Korea.\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1414, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1239, \"end\": 1246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing\", \"score\": 0.9999770015558951, \"rank\": 2.285139563413167e-05, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing\"}, {\"begin\": 1252, \"end\": 1258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\", \"score\": 0.8144801170727122, \"rank\": 0.2267627011054119, \"text\": \"Carver\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington_Carver\"}, {\"begin\": 1278, \"end\": 1286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Empire\", \"score\": 0.9829414714474103, \"rank\": 0.015871192608072394, \"text\": \"Imperial\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Empire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Empire\"}, {\"begin\": 1346, \"end\": 1351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2014_Winter_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9938881500416461, \"rank\": 0.006149434367656574, \"text\": \"Sochi\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2014_Winter_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2014_Winter_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1353, \"end\": 1359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999999410752043, \"rank\": 4.826703855717909e-08, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://